<title>Testing phrases</title>
<body>
<example><title>Example of phrase styles</title>This is a <b>bold</b> and <i>italic</i> and <u>underlined</u> phrase.
Now, combos: <b>bold <u>underlined</u> and <i>italic</i> and <tt><i><u>mono-ital-under</u></i></tt> <i>and</i> <tt>monospaced</tt>.</b><p>All
of the same things, in a paragraph:</p><p>This is a <b>bold</b> and <i>italic</i> and <u>underlined</u> phrase.
Now, combos: <b>bold <u>underlined</u> and <i>italic</i> and <tt><i><u>mono-ital-under</u></i></tt> and <tt>monospaced</tt>.</b></p></example>
<p>Phrase styles using i, b, u, tt::</p>
<ul>
